{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_01","textHome":"我叫环彩羽。因为刚来神滨市不久……@对神滨市了解的不是很透彻，@若是彼此间互有不熟悉的，希望能多多交流。@啊！话说……我的兴趣是做料理。@可以的话……我做晚饭给你吃好不好呀？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_18","textHome":"即使如今已经不是了，有朝一日@我也想向小忧坦白……曾经怯懦的自己。@因为我相信……小忧的话，@无论是怎样的我，都会温柔接纳的吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.1,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_19","textHome":"为了找回自己重要的东西……@我一定会一次又一次地变强！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":1}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_20","textHome":"接受弱小的自己……@从这里开始慢慢进步就好了吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_21","textHome":"开始一点点……慢慢改变了吗……？@即便厌恶过去的自己……也不能当作不存在……@应该接纳它，然后超越它……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_22","textHome":"和大家相遇之后，我终于明白了。@正因是重要的人，才不能隐藏自己的本心……@正因为重要，才必须传达出自己真实的心意。@因为对喜欢的人，是不应该说谎的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_23","textHome":"我不会再蒙混过关，也不会再欺骗自己了。@从自我保护的那层厚壳中飞出来后……@发现外面的世界好明亮，感觉浑身都轻松了。@我终于……成为了自己想要成为的人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_24","textHome":"嗯，一起加油吧？@因为我相信……只要互相支持，@就能够到达一个人到达不了的地方。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_25","textHome":"早上好。嗯……！@我喜欢早晨的问候，就像打开了开关一样，@涌出了「今天也要好好加油」的心情！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_26","textHome":"还没吃午饭的话，要一起吃吗？@我不太挑食……所以吃什么都可以。@有什么想吃的东西吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_27","textHome":"晚饭，已经做好了……不介意的话请尝尝吧？@味道太淡的话就告诉我哦？@我已经习惯了这个味道，@所以不确定会不会太淡了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_03","textHome":"小忧她无论何时……@都有办法让大家露出笑容呢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_28","textHome":"还没睡吗?@要是不打扰的话，我也陪你熬会夜吧。@虽然每天都这样，会对身体不好……@只是偶尔的话，这样熬夜也不要紧吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_29","textHome":"我呢，连饮食的喜好，@好像都跟周围的人不太一样……@像是炒豆渣啦、杂煮啦……@我都觉得朴素而美味……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_30","textHome":"我们也差不多该出门了……@嗯，我已经准备好了哦？@不用着急，我会耐心等着的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_31","textHome":"就算是漫长得没有尽头的道路……@我也不能放任魔女不管……！@没问题……我一定……不会迷茫的……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":1}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_32","textHome":"团队的强大……也就是羁绊的强大吧。@为彼此考虑的心情，@会成为无可替代的力量……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100,"motion":0}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_33","textHome":"最近都流行些什么？@作为中学生的我居然问出这种问题，@很奇怪吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_34","textHome":"大家在手机上写邮件的速度，好快啊……@吓到我了。我可是连壁纸怎么换都不知道……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_35","textHome":"妈妈的料理，确实是特别的呢。@不仅仅是美味……还让人感到莫名的安心……@大家也有这样的感觉吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":100100,"motion":200}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_36","textHome":"流行歌和电视剧……和同龄的孩子聊天时，@总是被不知道的东西所震惊。@我是不是该多了解一些比较好？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100,"motion":300}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_37","textHome":"桃子给人的感觉就是值得信赖的大姐姐。@其实对于枫和玲奈而言，@也正是姐姐一样的存在吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_04","textHome":"连我都开始说教别人了……@自己都有点难以置信……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_38","textHome":"只要和八千代她们在一起……@悲伤的情绪也会烟消云散……@无论是欢喜还是悲伤，@全部都……能和大家分享……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"c